.TH MNEMOSYNE-RETENTION-STATUS 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne retention-status \- Report candidate turn count without writing (always dry\-run).
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne retention-status\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Report candidate turn count without writing (always dry\-run).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Report candidate turn count + sample IDs without writing (default)
.TP
\fB\-\-apply\fR
Run the UPDATE tombstone on candidate turns (writes)
.TP
\fB\-\-days\fR
Retention window in days (default: MNEMOSYNE_CHAT_RETENTION_DAYS env or 90)
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR
KnowledgeGraph DB path (default: auto\-resolve)
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
